main event: Metal filings and strips were recovered on a farm in Iowa after a bursting flash was observed, believed to be associated with a UFO incident.
interesting points: The incident was reported about three weeks prior to the recovery of metal strips., The metal strips were tested and found to be slightly radioactive., The investigation concluded that the strips were chaff used by SAC in ECM training., A flash observed during the incident was likely a meteor., No photographs were present in the report.
